1
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,519
Hurry up

2
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,519
Go bring him to me

3
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:33,879
Whoa

4
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,560
You scared the life out of me

5
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,519
Do you have any idea

6
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:42,359
that you could scare someone to death?

7
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:43,680
How vulgar

8
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:45,840
Our master wants to see you

9
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,079
Follow me

10
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:49,680
Uncle is here too

11
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,400
Looks like today might pay off

12
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,040
If he truly has another identity

13
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,920
I'll have a powerful backer from now on

14
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,400
Uncle Tianxuan

15
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:01,319
Long time no see

16
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,680
I've missed you so much

17
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,719
You little rascal

18
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:04,959
Where the hell have you been?

19
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,719
Why is this old swindler here too?

20
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:12,439
So this is the Ning Chen praised by Imperial Father and Old General Chen?

21
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,120
He doesn't look like much

22
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:15,360
Sit down first, then we'll talk

23
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:17,639
Uncle

24
00:02:18,199 --> 00:02:19,280
You know this old swindler?

25
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,919
Old General Chen

26
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,360
has rendered great service to our court

27
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,360
His might is known far and wide

28
00:02:24,479 --> 00:02:26,840
Few people don't know who he is

29
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,280
You're a general?

30
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,199
What?

31
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,879
Don't I look the part?

32
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,599
Then why did you scam me that day

33
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,439
and got me beaten up for nothing?

34
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:42,080
I won't let you off today

35
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,520
A gentleman uses words, not fists.

36
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:48,439
Sit down, sit down.

37
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:50,080
Whatever it is, let's talk it out.

38
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,439
This man has some nerve.

39
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,520
In all the court, aside from Imperial Father,

40
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,319
no one dares treat the Old General this way.

41
00:02:57,479 --> 00:02:58,120
The other day,

42
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,800
you chose to help that person yourself.

43
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:02,879
You did the good deed on your own.

44
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:04,919
And you took that beating willingly.

45
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,240
What does it have to do with me?

46
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,719
You old swindler, trying to play dirty, huh?

47
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,400
Fine.

48
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,000
Then you owe me damages for emotional distress.

49
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,240
That fee, whatever it is,

50
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,360
I will pay it for him.

51
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,960
Today, just for my sake,

52
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:25,080
let Old General Chen off the hook.

53
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,639
Spends so generously,

54
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,960
attended by a eunuch,

55
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,520
and knows the Old General as well.

56
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:34,960
Uncle, you must be royalty without a doubt.

57
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:37,599
Then I'll gladly accept.

58
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,680
That's our Uncle Tianxuan!

59
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,080
Having a friend like this

60
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,919
is truly your blessing.

61
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,479
This man is quite interesting.

62
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:46,759
You flatter me.

63
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:50,639
By the way, who are these two?

64
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:51,879
My humble son,

65
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:53,599
and my beloved daughter.

66
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,240
Uncle, you have both a son and a daughter,

67
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,520
and great wealth besides.

68
00:03:58,719 --> 00:04:00,719
Your son is truly handsome and elegant.

69
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,639
Your daughter is truly as lovely as a flower.

70
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:05,840
And a virtuous and gentle

71
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,719
wife at home.

72
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:10,800
So,

73
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,439
Uncle, are you buying poems today?

74
00:04:14,719 --> 00:04:15,759
No poems today.

75
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,480
I came today

76
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,079
to bring you some good news.

77
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:20,639
The strategies you proposed the other day

78
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,920
to Old General Chen regarding the Tuluo Kingdom,

79
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,800
His Majesty has learned of them.

80
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,720
And he was furious.

81
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:28,800
What?

82
00:04:30,399 --> 00:04:30,959
I mean, greatly pleased.

83
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,079
His Majesty believes you are brilliantly talented

84
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,600
and exceptionally wise.

85
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:38,839
So he appointed you to the Imperial Inspectorate as a Silver Guard.

86
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,120
The Imperial Inspectorate?

87
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:43,360
The Inspectorate answers directly to Imperial Father.

88
00:04:43,839 --> 00:04:46,399
Does Imperial Father intend to bring Ning Chen under his wing?

89
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,360
Then wouldn't I lose my chance?

90
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:52,319
It seems His Majesty truly appreciates talent

91
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,040
and plans to cultivate Ning Chen.

92
00:04:56,079 --> 00:04:56,920
You little rascal,

93
00:04:57,319 --> 00:04:58,600
thrilled, aren't you?

94
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:01,079
The Inspectorate answers directly to His Majesty.

95
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,480
It has the power to oversee all officials

96
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,199
and the entire realm.

97
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,759
If at the Ning residence

98
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,759
you suffer any unjust treatment,

99
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:11,439
a single petition can reach the Emperor directly.

100
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,480
You can pin on him charges of a lax household

101
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,480
and cruel treatment of his son.

102
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,600
Oh, Ning Ziming!

103
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:20,800
Really?

104
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:21,920
Of course.

105
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,639
Thank you, Uncle Tianxuan.

106
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,519
No need to thank me.

107
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:28,040
You should thank His Majesty instead.

108
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:30,120
His Majesty?

109
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:34,079
But I have never even met His Majesty.

110
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,959
I wonder if a nobody like me

111
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,360
will ever have the chance.

112
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,360
Don't worry.

113
00:05:41,759 --> 00:05:43,600
You'll meet him sooner or later.

114
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,439
Ning Lanxing.

115
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,959
He actually knows my surname is Ning?

116
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,199
So Uncle Tianxuan already knew.

117
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,959
Lanxing is just my pen name.

118
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:59,439
The name I use when writing poetry.

119
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,160
In that case,

120
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,199
let me formally introduce myself.

121
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,519
I am Ning Chen.

122
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,879
A pleasure to meet you, Uncle Tianxuan.

123
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,360
Likewise.

124
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,800
So,

125
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,920
how much does a Silver Guard earn per month?

126
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,199
Are you that short on money?

127
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,959
Under the name Lanxing,

128
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,040
any poem you write sells for hundreds of taels.

129
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,439
Why bother joining the Inspectorate?

130
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:22,480
I am.

131
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,639
Of course I am.

132
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,879
Selling poems for money

133
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,439
isn't a long-term plan.

134
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,319
Besides,

135
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,240
I don't want to be just a scholar.

136
00:06:29,519 --> 00:06:30,519
My true ambition

137
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,079
is to earn merit on the battlefield,

138
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:34,160
to win a title in the saddle.

139
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,079
After all, I'm a soldier.

140
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,079
It's pretty much my line of work.

141
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:44,600
Good lad!

142
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,120
You've got ambition.

143
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:48,199
Hey...

144
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,879
What... what's wrong with you?

145
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,199
It's nothing.

146
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,279
I'm still a bit weak.

147
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,160
Still recovering.

148
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:57,600
You look so frail, you little rascal.

149
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,319
Drop by Chen Manor when you can.

150
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,639
I'll teach you some martial arts.

151
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,319
It'll build up your strength.

152
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,319
Really?

153
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,560
Thank you, Old General.

154
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,079
Why not "old scammer" anymore?

155
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,040
That's a separate matter.

156
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:14,920
You shouldn't have hidden your identity.

157
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:15,800
Actually,

158
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,920
I grew up hearing tales of your heroics.

159
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:19,399
My admiration for you

160
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,839
flows like a mighty river,

161
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:26,120
endless and unceasing.

162
00:07:26,839 --> 00:07:27,519
You little rascal.

163
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,120
When did you learn to flatter like that?

164
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,319
You've got quite the silver tongue.

165
00:07:31,079 --> 00:07:32,720
But I don't mind hearing it.

166
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,439
All right, that's enough.

167
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,160
It's getting late today.

168
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,079
Stop your prattling.

169
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,079
The decree for your Inspectorate appointment

170
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,240
should be reaching Ning Manor soon.

171
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,560
Hurry back to receive it.

172
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,399
All right.

173
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,600
Then, Uncle Tianxuan,

174
00:07:48,199 --> 00:07:48,839
Old General Chen,

175
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,480
brother,

176
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:51,680
sister,

177
00:07:55,399 --> 00:07:55,920
cousin,

178
00:07:57,439 --> 00:07:58,399
I'll see you all later.

179
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,519
You little rascal!

180
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,240
Don't forget to visit Chen Manor.

181
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,439
I won't forget.

182
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:07,879
Lao Quan.

183
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:08,720
Yes, Your Majesty.

184
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,720
It seems Ning Chen has suffered

185
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:12,000
quite a bit at home lately.

186
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:14,560
Drag Ning Ziming to the imperial study to see Us.

187
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,600
Yes, Your Majesty.

188
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,519
It seems if I want Ning Chen on my side,

189
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,879
I'll have to find another way.

190
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,879
What are you all doing here?

191
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,519
Ning Chen,

192
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,519
the manor's been overrun with rats lately.

193
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,279
For the safety of the household and its valuables,

194
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:38,080
we must search every room.

195
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,679
Guards!

196
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,559
Search this place thoroughly.

197
00:08:59,919 --> 00:09:01,759
Your humble servant greets Your Majesty.

198
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,519
Ning Ziming, I ask you this.

199
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:13,679
What kind of emperor am I in your eyes?

200
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,000
Your Majesty,

201
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:19,600
You are unmatched in civil and military achievements,

202
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:21,399
and are a benevolent and righteous sovereign.

203
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,159
A benevolent sovereign?

204
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,559
So what you mean is,

205
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,080
I have been too benevolent,

206
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,039
so you may defy my decrees?

207
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:31,120
Your servant would never dare!

208
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,600
Please enlighten me, Your Majesty.

209
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:36,320
I ordered you to treat Ning Chen well,

210
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,480
yet what have you done?

211
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,559
How did he get those injuries?

212
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:41,879
Is your minister's manor a den of thieves,

213
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,120
or a bandit's lair?

214
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:45,840
His Majesty has seen Ning Chen?

215
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:47,039
How could that be?

216
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,480
Old General Chen always keeps his word.

217
00:09:50,399 --> 00:09:51,879
Could someone have planted

218
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,879
a spy in my manor?

219
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,759
Forgive me, Your Majesty!

220
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:58,360
I beg Your Majesty's mercy!

221
00:09:58,519 --> 00:10:00,399
Mercy, mercy, mercy!

222
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:02,399
Mercy, please, mercy!

223
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,960
Mercy, mercy!

224
00:10:04,159 --> 00:10:05,360
Enough, enough, stop kowtowing!

225
00:10:05,519 --> 00:10:06,200
You...

226
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:06,960
I know,

227
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,679
you want to kowtow yourself to death here,

228
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:11,399
to brand me as a cruel ruler, is that it?

229
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,240
Your servant would never dare!

230
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,879
I would never dare.

231
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,559
Mark my words clearly:

232
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,600
if there is a next time,

233
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:22,240
I will personally send you to the execution ground.

234
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,720
Your servant will keep it in mind.

235
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,159
In mind, in mind.

236
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:27,799
Get out.

237
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:28,639
Yes.

238
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:32,360
Your servant takes his leave.

239
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:37,879
Shipeng.

240
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:39,879
Go to the Ning Manor once more.

241
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:43,039
Deliver the decree summoning Ning Chen to the Imperial Inspectorate.

242
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,080
Yes.

243
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:49,759
Fourth brother,

244
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,799
Big brother was thinking of you.

245
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,440
Just think,

246
00:10:52,759 --> 00:10:54,399
what if you got bitten by rats?

247
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,279
We could never face Father.

248
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,360
Exactly.

249
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:59,480
Big brother did it for your own good.

250
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,080
Big brother thinks of me,

251
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:04,480
so I shouldn't be ungrateful.

252
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,200
By the way,

253
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,440
I happen to have

254
00:11:06,679 --> 00:11:08,759
a very precious gift here,

255
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,960
to present to you, big brother.

256
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,360
Fourth brother is being sensible.

257
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,919
What precious gift could he possibly have?

258
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:25,519
Hurry.

259
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,159
Big brother

260
00:11:44,039 --> 00:11:44,759
Ning Chen

261
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:46,759
You beast

262
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,600
How dare you splash piss on me!

263
00:11:49,919 --> 00:11:51,759
This boy's urine wards off rats

264
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:52,759
And it can also cure illness

265
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,120
You should count yourselves lucky

266
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,759
It's just that I've been running a bit hot lately

267
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,679
The smell

268
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,799
Might be a bit strong

269
00:11:58,279 --> 00:11:58,759
I...

270
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:02,879
Big brother

271
00:12:03,799 --> 00:12:04,759
Hurry, help me get this off

272
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,440
Ouch, ouch, ouch

273
00:12:07,759 --> 00:12:08,919
Big brother, your head's too big

274
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,879
I can't get it off

275
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,360
You wretched scoundrel

276
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:15,799
I'm doing this for your own good

277
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:17,919
And yet you do something so disgusting

278
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:18,600
Guards!

279
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,320
Seize him!

280
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:19,960
Get him

281
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,440
Brothers, both of you

282
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,639
Think carefully

283
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,159
About how Lord Ning has treated me lately

284
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:27,399
If you injure me

285
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:29,360
Lord Ning will surely hold someone accountable

286
